  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657900/extras/f03ec6767c90858d7e512698b27754a3.poster.avif?t=1773898875\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657900/extras/f03ec6767c90858d7e512698b27754a3.webm?t=1773898875\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657900/extras/f03ec6767c90858d7e512698b27754a3.mp4?t=1773898875\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >\"Just another job. Shouldn't be too complicated.\"</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FOR SALE</strong> is a first-person horror adventure game with a strong emphasis on atmosphere and exploration. Interact with objects, take pictures using your digital camera, and discover unnerving secrets all while exploring a seemingly normal house. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A short and immersive exploration experience; </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Interact with objects, furniture, read notes and solve puzzles;  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Hidden collectibles, achievements and multiple endings; </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A nostalgic atmosphere inspired by PSX/PS2-era visuals, with handcrafted assets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657900/extras/74db5f90458e9cc67480f88f24e09681.poster.avif?t=1773898875\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657900/extras/74db5f90458e9cc67480f88f24e09681.webm?t=1773898875\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2657900/extras/74db5f90458e9cc67480f88f24e09681.mp4?t=1773898875\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > DISCLAIMER </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FOR SALE </strong>is intended to be played in one sitting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FOR SALE</strong> is best played with headphones on.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FOR SALE</strong> contains flashing lights which may not be suitable for people with photosensitive epilepsy.</p>",
